The real_corpus benchmark's no-regression gate loads perf-baseline.json by op name through load_baselines and baseline_for, treating each entry's median_ms and noise_floor_ms as the f64 baseline and additive noise floor for that op's regression threshold; an op absent from the JSON skips only the regression rule for that op, and a present entry missing either field panics.
